@rarebeauty ok need these in every color!!! 👄 This is shade Wonder, but here’s my full review
•it’s like a 3 - in - 1 product because you get the initial application, a stain, and as it wears it gets more pigmented/darker/brighter (which i loveeeee). If you noticed the first swipe on my lip was more pink, but in a matter of seconds it gets deeper, and after i filmed this it was almost red 👄
• some people say it feels like water when they apply, but i don’t get this feeling at all. It feels more similar to a gloss but it’s not sticky and way way more lightweight! I think the Sephora Collection lip stains feel more like water for comparison, if you’ve ever tried those!
• they give you glossy/juicy/full looking lips and I’m just obsessed with how they look on!!
• overall, this is a 10/10 for me✨
